<varlistentry id="options.MenuHiTitleStyle">
	<term>MenuHiTitleStyle <emphasis remap='I'>"style_name"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>AfterStep now allows you to specify a MyStyle to be used
		for the titlebar of the currently hilighted menu. AS soon as the menu goes out
		of focus its titlebar will be rendered using MenuTitleStyle.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
